{"tid":1933852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共 : 撤銷對李文亮的訓誡書 他是共產黨員 不是所謂的反體制人物","createTime":"2020-03-19T14:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T14:51:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecef130b78d5980193362c8a4c6def8f8d0035a","tid":1933852,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"國家監委：李文亮不是反體制人物 想煽風點火的人會得逞<br />\n<br />\n率先揭露武漢疫情並被公安指造謠的內地眼科醫生李文亮，上月初因感染新型冠狀病毒不治，國家監委調查組通報有關調查後，武漢市公安局決定撤銷對李文亮的訓誡書。調查組負責人又指，李文亮是工作認真負責的醫生，去年底轉發及發布「華南海鮮市場確診7宗沙士」的信息，主觀上是想提同學、同事注意防範，被大量轉後引發社會關注，客觀上對各方面重視疫情，加強防控起到推動作用。<br />\n<br />\n負責人又指，一些敵對勢力為攻擊中國政府及中共，為李文亮貼上對抗體制的「英雄」、「覺醒者」等標籤，是完全不符合事實；強調李文亮是共產黨員，不是所謂的反體制人物，那些別有用心的勢力想煽風點火、蠱惑人心、挑動社會情緒，注定不會得逞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275066&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275066%26csid%3D261_341&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3c9f48aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275066&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a919608f3792c16e71983bed54ee0c5510614ca5","tid":1933852,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/wearebluec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwearebluec&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4b9b1e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wearebluec</a><br />\n藍絲文宣group，入去report佢呀！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snxnQWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnxnQWC.jpg&h=f0b6ba5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0a0f193ccb0439ec1c775a19ecea9456515c28","tid":1933852,"uid":5103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br